data.description: Experience the allure of living in this exceptional 3 bdrms, 2 bths multifamily residence, situated in the sought-after N&W neighborhood of Richmond. Encompassing nearly 1300 sqft, this property seamlessly combines comfort with substantial investment potential. Ascend to the luminous & expansive 736 sqft upper duplex, featuring 2 welcoming bdrms, an updated bth rm, an open living room, & a well-appointed kitchen adorned w/quartz countertops. The dining room area boasts built-in cabinetry, adding a touch of sophistication. The generous private rear yard creates an urban oasis for relaxation and entertainment. The legal 550 sq ft Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU) on the lower level, completed in 2020, showcases a plethora of upgrades. Revel in the open living style room w/full kitchen; this 1 bdrm, 1 full bth home is complemented by its own private rear yard space. Driveway & a 1 car garage. Recent upgrades. This property not only provides a residence but also offers a lifestyle of ease and accessibility. Enjoy proximity to BART, 80 & 580 freeways, schools, parks, the Friday farmers market, & Civic Center shops. Seize this opportunity for a seamless and convenient lifestyle. Your new home awaits—schedule a viewing today & make every commute a breeze!
